window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Sacred vows. Brutal truths. And a campus king hell-bent on owning me.</b></p> <p>This town has become my nightmare, and Roman Rush is both my tormentor and my salvation. I've been drawn into his dark world, caught in his snare, and the more I pull against his control, the tighter his grip. I'm desperate to break free, but I have to stay for Bree. There's a mystery shrouding her that I'm determined to uncover.</p> <p>As my relationship with Roman intensifies, I discover something that brings my entire world crashing down—a dark truth that makes me question everything I thought I knew about Roman and the Sacred Sons…</p> <p><i>This is a dark academia college romance with mature themes. A complete list of content warnings can be found on the author's website. This is the third book in a four-book series, following the same couple, and ends on a cliffhanger.</i></p>"; 
